Bruno Barnabe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruno_Barnabe 0 Bruno Bianco Alberto G. G. Barnabe (3 April 1905 in London – June 1998 in Surrey) was an English film and stage actor. He performed in the West End, on Broadway, and in Egypt, Australia and New Zealand.
